                    <h2>About Us</h2>
                    <h5 class="style-h5"><strong>The consistent practice connects us with our inner beauty.</strong></h5>

                    <p>Radha and Jay Jayaraman have pursued spirituality since the early 1980s amidst professional careers and raising a family. They continue their journey into their 80s, actively engaged in spiritual service. They have organized Yoga programs and retreats across cities like Ottawa, Toronto, Montreal, New York, New Jersey, and Chicago.</p>
                    <p>Inspired by <strong>Dr. Sri Ganapathi Sachchidhananda Swamiji and Sri Datta Vijayananda Teertha Swamiji</strong>, they are certified teachers of Datta Kriya Yoga <a href="https://www.dattakriyayoga.org" target="_blank">(https://www.dattakriyayoga.org)</a> and contribute to wellness and meditation through simple lifestyle practices. Since the early 1980s, they have also taught Siddha Samadhi Yoga under Guruji Sri Rishi Prabhakar, focusing on self-development, meditation, health, and emotional equanimity.</p>
                    <p>Both Radha and Jay are certified teachers, they contribute to the community by systematically incorporating a life-style of simple practices.
                    Their passion is to <i><strong>"Show that one can be fully involved in today’s lifestyle and also lead a wholesome life of Yoga practice."</strong></p></i></p>
                </div>
                <div class="about_Right">
                    <img src="img/about/about0.jpeg" alt="Image 1" class="image_control">
                    <img src="img/about/about2.jpg" alt="Image 2" class="image_control2">
