                    <p><strong>Siddha Samadhi Yoga</strong> is the main program of the organization and being the Flagship Program has become synonymous with the name of the organization. Siddha is Knowledge that is proven and has been consistently accomplished. Samadhi Stands for Equanimous State of Intellect SSY adds inspiration/empowerment.</p>
